image_analysis.description: An interior shot of a highly stylized room featuring a blue and white color palette. The room contains a blue glass or acrylic table, two matching blue lamps with shell-like bases, a large gold-framed painting of a woman, blue floral wallpaper, and blue and white chevron-patterned curtains. A grey sofa and a patterned daybed are also visible. A large blue chandelier hangs from the ceiling.
image_analysis.layout: Interior room view with furniture and decor; a watermark/identifier is located in the bottom right corner.
